Come on, all those of you who made that decision, just repeat this prayer, but you're not gonna pray alone.

35:03.163 --> 35:05.746
Let's all pray together, say, Heavenly Father,

35:06.274 --> 35:09.278
Almighty God, I give you my life.

35:10.139 --> 35:11.461
I surrender my heart.

35:12.463 --> 35:18.632
Today I boldly declare Jesus as my Lord and my Savior.

35:19.312 --> 35:21.696
I am forgiven of all my sins.

35:22.797 --> 35:28.445
Fill me with your spirit so I can boldly share your love with others.

35:29.186 --> 35:30.348
Thank you for new life.

35:31.089 --> 35:32.111
Now you have mine.

35:32.872 --> 35:34.514
In Jesus name I pray.

35:34.850 --> 35:36.553
Can somebody get a little loud?

35:36.994 --> 35:38.998
Can somebody celebrate this goodness?

35:39.018 --> 35:39.338
Come on.

35:41.282 --> 35:44.668
We are celebrating with those of you who just made the decision to follow Jesus.

35:45.049 --> 35:47.714
Check out the show notes for helpful resources and next steps.

35:48.355 --> 35:54.386
Remember to head over to life.church slash podcast connect to share a little about yourself and how we can support you.

